original_body_lines: President Ranil Wickremesinghe, who was on a two-day official visit to India, arrived at the Bandaranaike International Airport (BIA) last night after completing this visit, the Airport Duty Manager said.
He welcomed the delegation of 17 people who went to New Delhi, India with the President on the official tour.
The President and the delegation arrived at the Airport at 11.25 p.m. yesterday from New Delhi, India, on SriLankan Airlines flight UL196. (T.K.G. Kapila)
